# Ex Cinere — Full Development Roadmap (MVP Focus)

This roadmap defines the staged implementation of the Ex Cinere simulation.

---

# 🧱 PHASE 1 — THE PROXIMITY ENGINE (BLE)

| Step | System | Goal |
|---|---|---|
| 1.1 | BLE Service | Implement background scanning/advertising for iOS & Android. |
| 1.2 | Bonding Logic | Detect ~10m proximity for 30s to trigger bond creation. |
| 1.3 | Chain System | Manage multi-link chains and shared buff calculation. |
| 1.4 | Anti-Cheat | Integrate accelerometer-based movement validation. |
| 1.5 | Sync Service | Store proximity state locally and sync to Supabase when online. |

---

