| Step | System | Goal |
|---|---|---|
| 2.1 | Survivor Model | Implement roles (Scout, Medic, Engineer, Cook, Guard). |
| 2.2 | Raid Engine | Asynchronous 2-minute commitment window resolution. |
| 2.3 | Hardcore Logic | Implement Level 1-99 progression and permanent death reset. |
| 2.4 | Loot System | Create BLE-broadcast loot chests with killer priority. |
| 2.5 | Defensive Gap | Implement the quadratic instakill bonus for low-level defenders. |

